{"type": "article", "id": 19903, "title": "有个房型不太正的豪宅，把自己设计成了很错落的样子", "description": "远近高低各不同啊。", "date": "2015-12-30T11:00:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11871, "name": "住宅"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 150, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120910qWEw9pzxXn1Y5oaj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>在韩国高阳市的住宅区，有一幢房子绝对过目难忘。房子外面罩了两层楼高的白色铝管栅栏，斜向排列围成圆弧形，像一圈波浪。透过这层栅栏能隐约看到里面的布置，有些地方是实体墙，有些是空的，似乎高低错落，别有洞天。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>白色围栏是从韩国传统的 “Cheoma” 屋顶演化而来的，但负责修建的</span>韩国 <a href=\"http://www.irojekhm.com/p_ke.htm\" target=\"_blank\">IROJE KHM Architects</a> 设计师也说，他从学校的铁栏杆中获得灵感。阳光透过栏杆照射到房间深处，也因为围栏的通透性，可以更好的融入小区环境。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>它真正的围栏是门口一米高的围墙，上面有大大小小的圆洞，类似于鹅卵石，也呼应了园林的意境。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120859gJjoV58Ek4xc3Gsq.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"950\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98958333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120900ryQdO0VnX8vH5jI3.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"685\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71354167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150242oDj6IrxaKfBnJbtU.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"678\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.70625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这所房子包括地下室一共有四层。地上的三层分成了左右两幢，中间隔了一个三角形的天井，用走廊来连通。天井的位置是整个住宅的花园，地面铺上了石子路，它位于一楼和二楼中间，进口后顺着楼梯就能走到。花园下面是另一个房间，在地下室和一楼的中间。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>这种错层结构延续在了整体建筑当中，室内室外布置了各式各样的楼梯，高低不一，角度也不同。让建筑本身有点像迷宫花园，移步换景，非常特别。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120900IG46jgOvZ8Q2TCAE.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1522\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.40925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120901nw0XhWvgENcVy3mL.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"633\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120901aHqOoEpQLmbuSYAe.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"638\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120901Wtm8lx71h03SyZTP.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"650\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67708333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120902AztPIC2qn0SQi7l1.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"644\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67083333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>“移步换景”的花园</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>因为三角形的天井和复合式的结构，大部分房间也都是不规则的，设计师取消了传统建筑中封闭的墙体和门窗，通过楼梯连接各个房间，营造出开放的环境。希望借此能让家庭成员有更多的互动和交流。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>二楼是客厅、餐厅等公共空间，三楼有书房、卧室，住在家中的人们能相互看到对方，但也能因错位的房间和而有一定的遮挡和距离。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120902qlYKvFke9jPbH4cD.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"648\" title=\"地下一楼\" alt=\"地下一楼\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>地下一楼的酒吧、储物间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120904Hlj4dfDv91Nahep7.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"648\" title=\"一楼\" alt=\"一楼\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>二楼厨房、餐厅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120905BPpNRZwuyMhzqA4U.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"656\" title=\" 一楼到二楼\" alt=\" 一楼到二楼\" data-ratio=\"0.68333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> 二楼到三楼音乐区</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021209051LBSJMXNpwy3erQP.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"639\" title=\"二楼\" alt=\"二楼\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>起居室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120906gr5UJpEXzBai4WZ8.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"664\" title=\"三楼\" alt=\"三楼\" data-ratio=\"0.69166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>三楼</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120906A69nMBRSid7Vbq1Y.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"639\" title=\"三楼书房\" alt=\"三楼书房\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>三楼书房</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120907CSid6vgXau4NTPmy.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120908fLHWbt7iw1xSkhvO.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"660\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t从屋顶俯瞰天井\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120908vscgJ6AZPjB3K1TI.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"690\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120908B5YwJyHGAsMOuknj.jpg\" width=\"682\" height=\"601\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.88123167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120909BnwKUGguYZPW95fS.jpg\" width=\"681\" height=\"581\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85315712\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120909lcdBUbnVriNfzvLo.jpg\" width=\"681\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.82232012\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120910ecxMDa82Pzifgywp.jpg\" width=\"681\" height=\"522\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76651982\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.gooood.hk/kyeong-dok-jai-by-iroje-khm-architects.htm\" target=\"_blank\">gooood</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}